ğŸ” 1. Auth / User APIs

Purpose: Login, role-based access

Method	Endpoint	                Description
POST	/auth/login	            Login user
POST    /auth/refresh           Refresh access token
GET	    /auth/me	            Get logged-in user profile
POST	/auth/logout	        Logout
PATCH	/auth/change-password	Change password


ğŸ¢ 2. Department APIs
Method	    Endpoint	                Description
POST	/departments	        Create department
GET	    /departments	        Get all departments
GET	    /departments/:id	    Get department by ID
PATCH	/departments/:id	    Update department
DELETE	/departments/:id	    Delete department
PATCH	/departments/:id/hod	Assign Head of Department


ğŸ“ 3. Student APIs
Method	        Endpoint	            Description
POST	        /students	            Create student
GET	            /students	            Get all students (filter by status, department)
GET	            /students/:id	        Get student details
PATCH	        /students/:id	        Update student
DELETE	        /students/:id	        Soft delete / suspend student
PATCH	        /students/:id/status	Change status (active, graduated, suspended)
GET	            /students/:id/courses	Student enrolled courses
GET	            /students/:id/payments	Student payment history
GET	            /students/:id/attendance	Student attendance


